*glib-2.32.4-r1 (04 Oct 2012)

  04 Oct 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +glib-2.32.4-r1.ebuild, -glib-2.32.4.ebuild,
  +files/glib-2.32.4-CVE-2012-3524.patch,
  +files/glib-2.32.4-clip-libc-enable-secure.patch:
  Security bump.
  Add a CLIP-specific patch to force usage of libc_enable_secure to check if we 
  are running in a privileged program, rather than simple uid checks.

