  -files/glib-2.26.0-disable-volumemonitor-broken-test.patch,
  -files/glib-2.25-punt-python-check.patch:
  Bump to latest. N.B. : depends on libffi, which used to 
  be a secondary package. Dependency renamed to 
  libffi-core in CLIP, to avoid conflicts against the
  secondary until it can be removed.

